{
  "stem": "10905.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister, my mother, my father, and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother's mother, my father's mother, who was supposed to be with us as well, because of a little bombing that happened and that the railway station was bombed in Subotica, they could not get out to come and join us.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So their fate was entirely different than ours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left Budapest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite crammed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for whatever reason, I don't know, two or three days they were haggling about letting us-- well, we were with this very, very special transport.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not supposed to go to concentration camp, we were leaving.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were gonna go to Uganda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were going to a neutral country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were going to go away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were going to be pawns, or a token of good faith, in a negotiation that were going on between Saly Mayer of the Joint Distribution Agency and a man called Kasztner and man called Joel Brand to save-- there was gonna be a devil with the bargain.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans desperately needed winterized trucks for the Eastern Front coming for the winter of '44.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were going to trade away and give up all the Jews for the trucks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there were almost, I mean, there were-- I think close to a million Jews still around in Hungary mainly at liberty.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they wanted a trade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the deal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean the deal was we were a part of the goodwill gesture that, as a matter of fact negotiations had continued.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
